      <title>德拉希竞相降低债务，标普下调 Altice 法国评级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/altice-france-rating-cut-by-s-p-after-moody-s-downgrade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Altice France SA 的信用评级在两天内第二次被下调，标普全球评级下调了这家陷入困境的电信公司的评级，进一步加大了持有该债务的抵押贷款债务的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/altice-france-rating-cut-by-s-p-after-moody-s-downgrade</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 16:20:19 GMT</pubDate>
